Package: ASURATBI
Type: Package
Title: A pipeline especially built for computing several single-cell datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Keita", "Iida", email = "kiida@protein.osaka-u.ac.jp",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1076-830X")))
Description: ASURATBI is a computational pipeline especially built for computing
    single-cell and spatial transcriptome datasets for our paper publications.
    ASURATBI is a developed version of ASURAT, using several informal packages
    and additional functions.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
